content: When you reach a fork in the road, you'll find two paths leading to the group of houses. The one on the right leads to the front, but there's also a Dragonfly Guai perched on a high ledge if you didn't kill him earlier that could be annoying. Taking the left path leads up to a back entrance, which may be preferable.

When you reach a fork in the road, you'll find two paths leading to the group of houses. The one on the right leads to the front, but there's also a Dragonfly Guai perched on a high ledge if you didn't kill him earlier that could be annoying. Taking the left path leads up to a back entrance, which may be preferable.
